com.aevi.payment

Class TransactionReferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aevi.payment.TransactionReferences

  • public final class TransactionReferences
extends java.lang.Object
    Part of a TransactionResult, this class contains identifier numbers associated with a transaction. These numbers can also be used to send a ReversalRequest.
